content: Archethect: Made significant contributions through two merged PRs this month, with PR #1482 introducing cross-chain swaps through Squid Router representing a massive code change (+154,950/-60,024 lines). Also fixed a core issue with PR #1473 by making modelConfiguration optional. Activity was sporadic, concentrated on just 2 days this month, with a primary focus on feature development (71%) and bug fixes (21%).
